{"tid":1514484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「不割席」從來只唔會對左膠講","createTime":"2019-08-28T18:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T01:22:10.000Z","uid":25240,"like":48,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2beffd1651e18f1e4c38added60969ad26b9afca","tid":1514484,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:18:02.000Z","msg":"今日見到何式凝班狗仔係立場出洗地文想幫甲級戰犯洗白<br />\n仲用「不割席」黎幫手擋<br />\n我第一個反應係 屌你老母臭閪呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先睇一睇fb 呢篇文<br />\n<br />\n我喺現場感受最深就係見到呢句「放核彈我都唔割蓆」。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家知道「不割蓆」的由來嗎？之所以有呢句說話，由一開始都係因為要保護義士。過往的抗爭，義士都會被割蓆、被出賣，所以今次先會講定畀你聽，今次唔好再同義士割蓆。</span></span><br />\n你只要曾經喺現場就會知班義士有幾勁，佢哋為你打生打死，你因為佢放火，就要同佢割蓆？荃灣有刀手無差別襲擊人，義士上前制伏，你又同佢割蓆？「不割蓆」唔係咁廉價㗎，「齊上齊落」唔係咁廉價㗎。<br />\n我唔同意「與怪獸對戰，唔好令自己變成怪獸」呢個論調，與怪獸對戰，如果你唔比佢更兇猛，你會死㗎！<br />\nSorry我真係唔會擔心有人鬧我，我只想講出我嘅想法。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「不割蓆、不分化、不篤灰」呢個口號，對我嚟講從來都係用嚟【保護義士】，而唔係泛民、左膠嘅防護罩。</span></span><br />\n何式凝尋日連累七十幾人被捕呀；<br />\n尹兆堅提出條例修訂呀，你明唔明條例修訂就係想呃你哋香港「袋住先」呀？如果「袋住先」，我哋就冇可能救到被捕義士㗎嘞！我哋以前都瀨過嘢㗎啦！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Sorry，「不割蓆」唔係用嚟保護呢班累死義士嘅泛民左膠。</span></span><br />\n唔准你哋責備義士，佢哋做嘅所有嘢，都係官迫民反！<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=372966126622869&amp;id=115540999032051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D372966126622869%26id%3D115540999032051&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=ac1d1a89\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=372966126622869&amp;id=115540999032051</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雨革當年就係大台班左膠糾察帶頭「捉鬼」交義士比popo <br />\n當年你班左膠又有冇諗過「不割席」呀 ？<br />\n而家淪為喪家之犬就出黎話「不割席 不分化」？ <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講緊你呀 Priscilla Sham <br />\n仆街啦 死左膠 <br />\n你地從來唔撚係同路人呀<br />\n屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D8x2kmJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD8x2kmJ.jpg&h=3ee7b0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156434856002023&amp;id=537382022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10156434856002023%26id%3D537382022&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=197ac491\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156434856002023&amp;id=537382022</a>"},{"pid":"c18c0143bb0a016c3aa20d80d741a6b865ea58f1","tid":1514484,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:20:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c9cd1d07c52b596a883d8ef0195d44187f93c6","tid":1514484,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:21:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2794a5ed25cabd7f94ad75759b8c07c41dda33","tid":1514484,"uid":293677,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:22:04.000Z","msg":"和理非 同 勇武 係自己人 係手足<br />\n左膠同中共一樣 係敵人"},{"pid":"3f60e1ddb6b7e471004f61560a75fa600ef63630","tid":1514484,"uid":25240,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4d2794a5ed25cabd7f94ad75759b8c07c41dda33","tid":1514484,"uid":293677,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:22:04.000Z","msg":"和理非 同 勇武 係自己人 係手足<br />\n左膠同中共一樣 係敵人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:24:21.000Z","msg":"講得啱<br />\n班死左狗次次柒撚完就扮和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2432bf7e1481047dd7649740e2dc6bf0d97fd1d7","tid":1514484,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:24:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80e7a533796775b1a098143d7661c4271c02fc2","tid":1514484,"uid":5